{"title":"iOS邮件客户端设置","author":"Mr.Hope","time":"2021年12月3日","shareable":true,"content":[["text",{"type":"tip","text":["以下步骤将指导您在 iPhone 的邮件客户端上添加学校邮箱。","本教程以原生(自带)邮件客户端为例"]}],["ul",{"text":["选择 “密码与账户”"]}],["img",{"src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-1.jpg"}],["ul",{"text":["选择 ”添加账户“"]}],["img",{"src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-2.jpg"}],["ul",{"text":["点击其他"]}],["img",{"src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-3.jpg"}],["ul",{"text":["选择 “添加邮箱账户”"]}],["img",{"src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-4.jpg"}],["ul",{"text":["输入账号密码，全名和描述可自行填写"]}],["img",{"src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-5.jpg"}],["ul",{"text":["按图示填写即可，邮箱账户和邮箱密码请填写自己对应的账户与密码"]}],["text",{"type":"tip","text":["尽管学校支持 \"smtp.nenu.edu.cn\"，但是因为证书不符无法在原生邮件客户端上添加。","在学校解决证书问题前，建议使用 163 企业邮提供的服务器。"]}],["img",{"src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-6.jpg"}],["ul",{"text":["在最后一步点击存储，即可完成邮箱账户的添加，之后打开自带的邮件 App 即可查看邮件。"]}]],"cite":[],"id":"guide/account/mail/ios","images":["https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-1.jpg","https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-2.jpg","https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-3.jpg","https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-4.jpg","https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-5.jpg","https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail/ios-6.jpg"]}